{"tid":1037262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國兩艘軍艦通過台灣海峽","createTime":"2019-02-25T20:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T00:38:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2648127bc7d4114a4ea76530a1a12b0fb58b5835","tid":1037262,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T20:38:52.000Z","msg":"美國兩艘軍艦通過台灣海峽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1444719-20190226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1444719-20190226.htm&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=4b03bd54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1444719-20190226.htm&h=5f243387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1444719-20190226.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兩艘軍艦星期一通過台灣海峽，美軍太平洋艦隊發表聲明說，行動展現美國致力維護印太地區的自由與暢通。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部，將繼續在國際法容許的任何地方飛行和航行。<br />\n<br />\n兩艘軍艦分別是「史塔森號」驅逐艦和「查維斯號」後勤彈藥補給艦。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，美方無視中國反對，增加軍艦通過台海的頻率，將令中美緊張關係加劇，亦可能被台灣視為特朗普政府的支持表態。"},{"pid":"c714639b6d8b6ab69e665f9d1921d973460bd27f","tid":1037262,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T20:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqeNrWa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqeNrWa.gif&h=b37b3d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍來了我帶路😂🤙🤙🤙"},{"pid":"a1c2edfc91ad890297b7609107c7fd71ffdb31c0","tid":1037262,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T20:40:06.000Z","msg":"help push"},{"pid":"aa2c9187f3416607d435893eb39585d48ec91c7f","tid":1037262,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T20:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d20c8e2bdf055c849da057959b6fc2ebc7efa1f","tid":1037262,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"